#. <CLT 04>こうして２人でこの景色を見るのも<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>今日で最後か…<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I decided to talk to Taka one more time before we all\n"
"left...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>色々と無茶苦茶なサバイバル生活だったけど<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>改めて振り返ってみると…楽しかったな。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I wonder if this is the last time we'll ever see this\n"
"place...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>なんだかんだ言っても、<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>人が死ぬような事態にはならなかったし。<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The time we spent here didn't make much sense,\n"
"but...looking back, I can't say I didn't have fun.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. まさかこんな何事もなく終わっちゃうとは…
#. 大仰に始まったわりにこの結末は地味だよね。
msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>There are still some mysteries left. What was\n"
"Monokuma, really? Why'd we end up here?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. もうちょっとこう、生きるか死ぬかみたいな
#. 壮大なスペクタクルを期待してたんだけどなぁ。
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I still don't have answers, but I'll have time to\n"
"figure all that out once we escape...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. ボクはこの島で希望を目にするためなら
#. 殺しても殺されても構わないと思ってたのに。
msgctxt "0006"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. それがどうだい？
#. このまったく生温い結末は…
msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"Taka... We're about to get out of here, but you don't\n"
"look too happy about it."
msgstr ""

#. …悪かったな、生温い事に付き合わせて。
msgctxt "0008"
msgid "Makoto... Don't laugh, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. あはは、日向クンはせっかちだなぁ！
#. ちゃんと話は最後まで聞いてくれないと！
msgctxt "0009"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. ボクはね、こんな事に巻き込まれたのは
#. 最高の不運だと思ってたんだ。
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "I'm...scared."
msgstr ""

#. だからこそきっと、この島で素晴らしく
#. 幸運な出来事が起こるんだろうって！
msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"Here, we have structure, order, discipline. What's\n"
"waiting for us out there...?"
msgstr ""

#. そして、だからこそ…戸惑ってるんだよ。
msgctxt "0012"
msgid "I don't see it as just escaping, you know?"
msgstr ""

#. 果たしてこの結末こそが幸運なのか…
#. それとも更なる不運なのか…
msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"Couldn't you say that as students, we're protected by\n"
"the school?"
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、日向クンはどっちだと思う？
msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"That's what I started thinking about while we were\n"
"sealed up in here."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>そんな事、俺に訊かれてもな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I see...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. わからない
msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Graduating from high school and going out into the\n"
"world definitely takes courage...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. さぁ…俺にはわからないよ。
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "But still... I know we can't just stand here!"
msgstr ""

#. そういわずに、どっちか答えてみてよ。
msgctxt "0018"
msgid "I think I learned that here, too..."
msgstr ""

#. ここまでボクに付き合ってくれたキミになら
#. きっとわかるはずだよ。
msgctxt "0019"
msgid "Taka..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>そう言われてもなぁ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"I still hate geniuses! That definitely hasn't\n"
"changed...!"
msgstr ""

#. 幸運
msgctxt "0021"
msgid "But other parts of me *have* changed."
msgstr ""

#. 幸運…だったんじゃないか？
msgctxt "0022"
msgid "All that matters is that I keep pushing forward!"
msgstr ""

#. 来た時の状況を考えたら、
#. 生きて無事に帰れるってだけでもさ。
msgctxt "0023"
msgid "I had it all wrong, you know..."
msgstr ""

#. …本当に？
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"I always thought that showing emotion, showing concern\n"
"or pain, was a sign of weakness."
msgstr ""

#. この程度の事が幸運だなんて
#. キミは本当にそう思うのかい？
msgctxt "0025"
msgid "But that's not true at all."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>狛枝はそうは思ってないって事か…<CLT>
msgctxt "0026"
msgid "And you taught me that...!"
msgstr ""

#. 不運
msgctxt "0027"
msgid "Thank you, Makoto! You don't know how grateful I am!"
msgstr ""

#. お前の言うこの温い結末も
#. 結局、不運…なのかもな。
msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"This place was strange, definitely. But I also learned\n"
"a lot while I was here."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0029"
msgid "So I'm glad I got to spend my time here!"
msgstr ""

#. …日向クン、ボクはこの島こそが
#. ボクの死に場所じゃないかと思ってたんだ。
msgctxt "0030"
msgid "I...feel the same way."
msgstr ""

#. おぼろげな希望だけを頼りに不運と幸運を
#. 繰り返す人生からやっと解放されるって…
msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"Our time here was bizarre, that's for sure. But we\n"
"built some good memories, too."
msgstr ""

#. ボクはいつもどこか、手の届く場所、
#. 目に見える範囲に希望を探してた。
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"Which is why I have to believe this isn't the last\n"
"time we'll see each other."
msgstr ""

#. でも、今は…違う。
msgctxt "0033"
msgid "...Makoto!"
msgstr ""

#. この島でキミと過ごした日々が教えてくれた。
#. 希望は始めから…このボクの中にもあったんだ。
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

#. なら、それに気付く事ができたのは
#. 幸運なんじゃないのか？
msgctxt "0035"
msgid "I need you to promise me something!"
msgstr ""

#. そう考えるところが素人の甘いところだよ！
msgctxt "0036"
msgid "You do...?"
msgstr ""

#. だって、自分の中の不確かなものなんて
#. どうやって探せばいいんだい？
msgctxt "0037"
msgid ""
"Remember what I told you before? About taking aim and\n"
"doing our best together!?"
msgstr ""

#. それでもボクは知ってしまったんだ。
#. いつでもこの胸に希望があるって…
msgctxt "0038"
msgid "Oh, um..."
msgstr ""

#. なら、もうそう簡単に死ぬだの殺すだの
#. 言えなくなったよな。
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "What was it again?"
msgstr ""

#. 自ら希望を消すのはお前の本意じゃないだろ？
msgctxt "0040"
msgid "What was it again?"
msgstr ""

#. …ほんと、まったくひどい不運だよ！
msgctxt "0041"
msgid "Wh-Wh-Wh—!?"
msgstr ""

#. だからそろそろ、少しくらい幸運に恵まれても
#. いいんじゃないかなと思うんだ。
msgctxt "0042"
msgid "Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh—!?"
msgstr ""

#. だから…今なら言えるかな、って。
msgctxt "0043"
msgid "WHAAAAAT!? Did you seriously forget!?!?"
msgstr ""

#. 言えるって…何をだ？
msgctxt "0044"
msgid "We talked about it SO MUCH! You! You're just—just—!"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Oh, crap...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 日向クン…
msgctxt "0046"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I'd better remember! I feel like he might flip out on\n"
"me any second!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. ボクと、友達になってくれるかい？
msgctxt "0047"
msgid "Defeat the geniuses!"
msgstr ""

#. え………？
msgctxt "0048"
msgid "Defeat the geniuses! ...Right?"
msgstr ""

#. ああ…なんだ。
msgctxt "0049"
msgid "In a general sense, I guess you could say that!"
msgstr ""

#. …そんなことで、よかったのか…
msgctxt "0050"
msgid "But no, not exactly! Did you forget what I said!?"
msgstr ""

#. もちろん…お安い御用だ。
msgctxt "0051"
msgid "N-No, I just...! I mean, you said..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>差し出された手をしっかりと握る。<CLT>
msgctxt "0052"
msgid "Keep trying and the world will reward you!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>今の狛枝となら、いつかちゃんとわかり合える日が<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>来るかもしれない。<CLT>
msgctxt "0053"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. <CLT 04>この島に来るまで感じた事もない、<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>明るい想いが俺の胸を満たしていた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0054"
msgid "Keep trying your best, and the world will reward you!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>これを"希望"と呼ぶのかはわからない。<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>でもこの想いがあるから俺は…歩いていけるだろう。<CLT>
msgctxt "0055"
msgid "THAT'S RIGHT! And I want you to help me achieve that!"
msgstr ""

#. はい
msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"Wait, what? But...that's just like, a figure of\n"
"speech, right?"
msgstr ""

#. いいえ
msgctxt "0057"
msgid "No! It's more than that!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>他にも話しかけたい人がいますか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0058"
msgid "This world doesn't belong to the geniuses."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>こうして俺たちの<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>南の島での生活は終わりを告げた――<CLT>
msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"Try hard enough, and your efforts WILL pay off. I'll\n"
"see to that myself!"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0060"
msgid "And to do that..."
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0061"
msgid "...I've decided to become a politician!"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Oh, wow...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0063"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>His grandpa was a politician, so I'm sure he has what\n"
"it takes to become one, too.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0064"
msgid ""
"Why are you standing there like this doesn't concern\n"
"you? You have to become a politician, too!"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0065"
msgid ""
"Together we can advocate for my ideas and change this\n"
"country!"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0066"
msgid ""
"Whaaaat!? No, no way! There's no way I could become a\n"
"politician! Totally impossible!"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"In the face of effort, NOTHING is impossible!\n"
"Hahahaha!"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0068"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Taka's face was shining with an inner glow...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I saw then that no matter what darkness might stand\n"
"before him, he would shine through it.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0070"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>He stood there, smiling, talking about the future he\n"
"was going to create.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0071"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>And I realized that it was one of many shapes that\n"
"hope could take...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0072"
msgid "<CLT 23>You received<CLT><CLT 3> <CLT><CLT 23><CLT><CLT 3>Kiyotaka's Undergarments<CLT> <CLT 23>as a present.<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0073"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0074"
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0075"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Is there anyone else you'd like to talk to?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. JAPANESE LINE NOT FOUND
msgctxt "0076"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>And that's how my school life at Hope's Peak Academy\n"
"came to an end...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
